M4yiAivjgUo/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FofM4yiAivjgUo%2Fgiphy.gif&h=494d36d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n柏祖,英格蘭著名舞者,曾在足總杯決賽跳出求勝舞助曼聯取得冠軍"},{"pid":"e83ad55e79c35c1159f708251a7b07eee74dc831","tid":947192,"uid":11270,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T06:04:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i4.chroniclelive.co.uk/incoming/article1357709.ece/ALTERNATES/s615/newcastle-united-manager-alan-pardew-shakes-sir-alex-ferguson-by-the-hand-before-the-game-715334471.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi4.chroniclelive.co.uk%2Fincoming%2Farticle1357709.ece%2FALTERNATES%2Fs615%2Fnewcastle-united-manager-alan-pardew-shakes-sir-alex-ferguson-by-the-hand-before-the-game-715334471.jpg&h=5d5cccbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來費sir一早欽點咗柏祖做下一任領隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98e6b271a08cb69c58d6b0548bece9591f671508","tid":947192,"uid":11270,"like":20,"dislike":3,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T06:10:07.000Z","msg":"講真<br />\n我唔知以前既柏祖帶超過三季波係點<br />\n只係知佢有性格都有成績<br />\n再睇佢既 YOUTUBE 跳舞片<br />\n純粹講個種 PASSION<br />\n直情係 HYPER 兼年輕版既費SIR<br />\n<br />\n大家都知曼聯更衣室又要變<br />\n又要建立新既秩序<br />\n大家同時又好驚柏祖既舞技會摧毀晒曼聯所有既排舞室<br />\n個種矛盾搞到大家都好想柏祖快手幫手換代引援同時又好想佢教三季就走<br />\n<br />\n但由賽後訪問黎睇<br />\n我係度諗 4年前佢就係費SIR指定既接班人<br />\n4年過去 阿SIR終於離開曼聯 柏祖歷盡鉛華 人生不在初相逢<br />\n一個大勝不驕 步步為營 同時足球智慧熱情還在頂峰既柏祖<br />\n會唔會就係個個我地心目中既新阿SIR"},{"pid":"55c2336e33ea38cdcec25b0927030c0d1192ac89","tid":947192,"uid":11270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T06:20:26.000Z","msg":"el Tav<br />\n@elTav<br />\n MUFC need a manager without fear to give them a team that plays without fear.  Controversial but..Pardew is the right mix of bravado &amp; ego.<br />\n<br />\nBT<br />\n@TheTeamForMe<br />\n Alan Pardew is a better manager then Louis Van Gaal<br />\n<br />\ntwitter開始有唔少呼聲要求柏祖上任<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_y.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6d4546190c6db8d8db4d5269cfa4a23f2da139b","tid":947192,"uid":11270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T06:24:20.000Z","msg":"Pardew predicts that Lindelof will struggle in the Premier League<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.football365.com/news/pardew-predicts-that-lindelof-will-struggle-in-the-premier-league\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.football365.com%2Fnews%2Fpardew-predicts-that-lindelof-will-struggle-in-the-premier-league&d=jwGvS68r2ymNx0b%2BIwoJjdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=4c4bf703\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.football365.com/news/pardew-predicts-that-lindelof-will-struggle-in-the-premier-league</a><br />\n<br />\n柏祖又中!"},{"pid":"3556dd315d91a6953db0617f98c63f4357325f84","tid":947192,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T06:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/BackInnocentIridescentshark-max-1mb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FBackInnocentIridescentshark-max-1mb.gif&h=987cb89e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0dd37e90f25af34d8eae41c7dd330149e2dd701d","tid":947192,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c87530c17a41d11e09a655ff557f51c5afb3085b","tid":947192,"uid":11270,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:57:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/ofM4yiAivjgUo/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FofM4yiAivjgUo%2Fgiphy.gif&h=494d36d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n柏祖,英格蘭著名舞者,曾在足總杯決賽跳出求勝舞助曼聯取得冠軍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T06:25:54.000Z","msg":"同一班黑人一齊跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d9b82d9c3c11e214766f29e75f0052c0af49413","tid":947192,"uid"